# CommunionHub 🎉

CommunionHub is a modern **event-based platform** designed to bring people together through faith, social, and charity events. The platform allows users to explore, filter, and add events while maintaining a **clean, responsive, and ultra-modern UI**.

## 🚀 Features

✅ **Fully Responsive UI** – Designed with a clean, ultra-modern interface  
✅ **Event Management** – View, filter, and add new events dynamically  
✅ **Authentication** – Secure login/logout functionality using JWT tokens  
✅ **Testimonials Section** – Engaging user reviews displayed in a smooth carousel  
✅ **Dark & Light Navbar** – Conditional navbar styling for a seamless experience  
✅ **Framer Motion Animations** – Smooth transitions for better UI engagement  
✅ **Footer Section** – A common footer included across all routes  

